events.text: You sure this is save, right?

As far as we understand, test subject seems to have their own communication system,
We have taken enough data from it so that we are able to make a translation system.
After many generations, the translation system can now pricisly understand and communicate with the test subjects.

Therefore I think it is the right time to begin the next step of the test. 
To determine if the test subjects have actual usage.
Well, that's the reason why we begin this whole project anyway.
